{
  "stem": "23742.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Bodies were floating in on the tide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the beaches were covered with wounded and the dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And on June the first, we were told to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] destroy our equipment, to destroy our units and our bikes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we should walk towards Dunkirk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "At that time, we were just on the French-Belgium border in a town called Lapan.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And on the morning of June the 1st, we began walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was seven miles where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we got to the port some time in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there was just one boat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was an old paddle steamer, you know, with the paddles rotating at the side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we managed to get on board.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Again, we were bombed and machine gunned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Eventually, the boat managed to get out of the dock and made its way across the channel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Again, we were bombed and machine gunned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "A couple of Spitfires came out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I remember them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They escorted us back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And eventually, we arrived at Folkeston.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We were glad to be home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I survived it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the unit was reformed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the next thing I did, I got married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- my wife and I, we were married on the 21st of June, 1940, at the Devonshire Road Synagogue in East London.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The service took place during an air raid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the reception that followed was adequate for the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Food was rationed, so we did as best we could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my parents did as best they could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after two days leave, I went back to my unit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from then onwards, I was part of the defenses of the UK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were operational.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
